  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3515790/extras/e095f3af3652441b96e0ddf1830d0168.avif?t=1742034054\" width=534 height=276 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Same old, same old to produce even more</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Capybara Achievement Clicker is an incremental and idle game that puts you in the shoes of a Capybara owner who earns more money with every click on his pet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The most capitalist Capybara</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With a total of more than a hundred achievements, with unrivalled simplicity, you can add a 100% game to your list.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A game to add to your 100%.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3515790/extras/fb55c5a15f8bfcfac9239510aebc78a8.avif?t=1742034054\" width=462 height=174 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Capybara with hats and apples</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect money and spend it to earn even more and more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over +100 easy achievements.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A game that's easy to set to 100%.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3515790/extras/b234dd8f7bf7d20f6b8a758874462acb.avif?t=1742034054\" width=800 height=184 /></span></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3515790/extras/e095f3af3652441b96e0ddf1830d0168.avif?t=1742034054\" width=534 height=276 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Same old, same old to produce even more</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Capybara Achievement Clicker is an incremental and idle game that puts you in the shoes of a Capybara owner who earns more money with every click on his pet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The most capitalist Capybara</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With a total of more than a hundred achievements, with unrivalled simplicity, you can add a 100% game to your list.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A game to add to your 100%.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3515790/extras/fb55c5a15f8bfcfac9239510aebc78a8.avif?t=1742034054\" width=462 height=174 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Capybara with hats and apples</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect money and spend it to earn even more and more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over +100 easy achievements.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A game that's easy to set to 100%.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3515790/extras/b234dd8f7bf7d20f6b8a758874462acb.avif?t=1742034054\" width=800 height=184 /></span></p></li></ul>",
